ActFirst Nations Commercial and Industrial Development Act
PrecisEnactment of the FORT McKAY FIRST NATION OIL SANDS REGULATIONS which establish, in respect of lands that are part of Fort McKay Indian Reserve No. 174C in Alberta, a legal framework governing the mining of oil sands and related activities that is harmonized with the laws of the Province of Alberta.
